{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Great Coffee Caper</strong> is a cute and cozy RPG where it's up to Detective Hootsworth to figure out who stole the town's coffee beans! Uncover clues in fast-paced clue battles, question the charming townsfolk, and figure out hoooo dunnit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529910/extras/steam_aboutheader.gif?t=1740158159\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On a dark and stormy night, a terrifying fiend stole all of the coffee beans in the town! His tall top hat and spine-chilling roar are sure to send the nearest tortoise shivering in their shell! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Never fear, Detective Hootsworth is on the case!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover clues, question the charming townsfolk, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Catch the thief and solve the mystery in <strong>The Great Coffee Caper</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529910/extras/hootsmouse_walk_talk.gif?t=1740158159\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529910/extras/steam_featureheader.gif?t=1740158159\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A cute, retro-inspired world to explore!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A cast of delightful and humorous townsfolk!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow trails with your spark glass!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast-paced clue battles! (akin to the bullet-hell genre)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">AND MORE!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;...hey! where's the stuff for &quot;AND MORE!&quot;?...&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;...what do you mean we can't show everything?!...&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;...ok fine! I